N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8129.03 - City of North Tonawanda

State Regulations
(a) Robinson

Street. The eastbound and westbound roadways of Robinson Street between River

Road, Route 266, and a point 0.1 mile east of Route 266. (b) [Eff. until Oct. 16, 1993, see also subd. (b) below.] Ward Road. Ward Road between River Road, Route 265, and the
driveway to Superior Lubricants. (b) [Eff. Oct. 16, 1993, see also subd. (b)
above.] Goundry Street. Goundry Street between Route 265 and Oliver

Street. (c) Route 425. Route 425
between Erie-Niagara county line and Nash Road. (e) Route 384. Route 384 between the

Erie-Niagara county line and Route 265. Notes
